headline: Jane Hunter's Exclusive Wine Dinner at The Ritz-Carlton, Bali
summary: The Ritz-Carlton, Bali is proud to present an unforgettable evening of culinary excellence and world-class wine at Jane Hunter's Wine Dinner, hosted at The Beach Grill on Thursday, 5 June 2025.
